<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>213</hymn_number>
<title>RATPI HNA CH213</title>
<key>Ab</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Ngai tuah ramlak khuamui chungah, Tuukhal pa au kha na theih lai, Tuu
 run chungin a tlaumi tuu, A kawh lengmang nak hna aw cu.

[C1]
   Ratpi hna, Ratpi hna! Sual nak hmun khan hun chuahpi hna! A tlaumi
   tuu vialte! Jesuh sinah cun ratpi hna.

[V2]
 A tlaumi tuu kha kawl awkah, Tuukhal pa hodah a bawm lai? Khuasih
 lonak tuu kawm chungah, Ho dah tuu a luhter hna lai?

[C2]
   Ratpi hna, Ratpi hna! Sual nak hmun khan hun chuahpi hna! A tlaumi
   tuu vialte! Jesuh sinah cun ratpi hna.

[V3]
 Ramlak le tlangcung zongah khan, Annih tahnak aw kha ngai tuah, Bawipa
 nih nan sin-ah a chim, &quot;Ka tuu kha na kawllai&quot; a ti.

[C3]
   Ratpi hna, Ratpi hna! Sual nak hmun khan hun chuahpi hna! A tlaumi
   tuu vialte! Jesuh sinah cun ratpi hna.</lyrics>
</song>